channel.title: Aurora 474 - Remake
channel.description:
[center][img]http://i61.tinypic.com/66f0vm.png[/img][/center] Welcome to the official Aurora 474 Development Team Thread, I decided to start development of the server after playing an 06 remake for a few weeks. Although i soon got bored due too lack of content such as bosses and minigames. That's why i decided to make a remake based on my favourite time on RuneScape, (Shortly after the release of The God Wars Dungeon).
[center][b]Server Details[/b] [b]Base:[/b]Project Insanity [b]Client Base:[/b] Galkons Refactored [b]Revision:[/b] 474 [b]XP Rate:[/b] 15x [/center]
[hr] [b][u]Changelog[/u][/b] [20/02/2014]Added all NPC Drops too Lumbridge along with 85% perfect global spawns and 90% perfect shops. [21/02/2014]Re-wrote Slayer, Each master gives different tasks varying in difficulty and task amount. [21/02/2014]Added some NPC Drops to some Slayer Monsters. [21/02/2014]Purchased Domain and hosting and set up a website. [22/02/2014]Added 100% Mining with perfect prospecting, All rocks and Pure Essence. [22/02/2014]Added teleport to Pure Essence [23/02/2014]Added custom Slayer master too assign extreme tasks such as Jad, GWD Bosses and KBD. [24/02/2014]Started to re-write Farming.
[hr] [center] [b]A Few Images[/b]
[img]http://puu.sh/79dBb.jpg[/img] [img]http://puu.sh/79dKV.jpg[/img] [img]http://puu.sh/79dNt.jpg[/img] [img]http://puu.sh/79dQM.png[/img] [/center][hr]
